Class Map

  • java.lang.Object
    • Gui.Map

  • public class Map
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a map. a map is an object that receives an image of an area, and the gps points of the top left and bottom right corners of the image. it will also same the value of how much pixels are in the image. as heightXwidth.
    Author:
    Alex vaisman, Shay naor.
